{"tid":1836013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係武漢手持午餐肉就有閪屌既日子","createTime":"2020-01-23T05:12:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T06:07:15.000Z","uid":150842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8380f641cf68c33c7c027a8c2f2cf8c2c1a2ccad","tid":1836013,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3931905102484342a7b2e42a34dba9ea962e3102","tid":1836013,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:17:34.000Z","msg":"屎眼岩唔岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3713998dc21bf41b80adeeb10e2fa9390646fac7","tid":1836013,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"有毒照屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1339e8f620de5961146a7917f4fff12ef8d153","tid":1836013,"uid":211549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"想比樓主屌"},{"pid":"035e92d96024a985ddd08adb106e5c249c9498ab","tid":1836013,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:22:10.000Z",